data.description: Attention Freeland area home buyers  Built by Cobblestone Builders, the areas premier home builder, featuring a whole home built in air purifying system, newer high efficient furnace, new dishwasher, second story laundry and gorgeous luxury, waterproof vinyl plank flooring. The new solid wood door makes this home stand out and the plush and stunning landscape throughout gives great privacy in the summer!    The pictures truly speak for themselves.   Everything in the home is negotiable including the Honda Pioneer 700-4 deluxe side by side, pool table, wall mounted TV's, furniture and backyard playscape.  Don't miss your chance to live in the areas highly sought after Springwood Subdivision with many kids and wonderful families!
